## Hardware
- ESP32 / Raspberry Pi
- L298N Motor Driver
- DC Motors(Servors)
- Ultrasonic Sensor
- Battery Pack
- Wheels + Chassis
- Jumpers
- IR sensors
- Buzzer
- LED

## Software
- Python 3
- GPIO libraries
- WiFi/Bluetooth control software



